  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"annotation-experimental-1.3.1\" data-text=\"Version 1.3.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.3.1</h3>\n<p>June 21, 2023</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.annotation:annotation-experimental:1.3.1</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/f8300b4e1477f08c1afcc8f8934161775573b395..c4344de87983c44f9ae3fdfb235801f65ac42830/annotation/annotation-experimental\">Version 1.3.1 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Place annotation at the beginning of the modifier list when applying lint auto-fix. (<a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issue?id=251172715\">b/251172715</a>)</li>\n<li>Use lint check to discourage use of <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.annotation.RequiresOptIn</code> in Kotlin sources (<a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issue?id=241097743\">b/241097743</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"annotation-experimental_version_130_2\" data-text=\"Annotation-Experimental Version 1.3.0\" tabindex=\"-1\">Annotation-Experimental Version 1.3.0</h2>",
